<h3>
  The former package Smash
</h3>
<p>
  The package "smash" had already been superseded by the
  GAP&nbsp;3 share package "<a href="matrix.html">matrix</a>"
  and hence has not been transferred to GAP&nbsp;4.
  The Smash functionality is (mostly) available as part of the
  GAP&nbsp;4 library.
</p>

